          <p>I used Devise for authentication, so the rest of the Devise user fields are also there but I didn't show them because that would be boring.</p>

          <p>I only allowed one phone number per user, with the thought that I will eventually add a texting feature to the app. I wanted to limit to one phone, but if I need to in the future could change that relationship to allow multiple phones per user.</p>

          <p>Each user can track many locations and see future ISS passes for each location. That way, if you travel or have a buddy across the globe or just like picturing the ISS sailing over a distant land you can know exactly when that will happen.</p>

